data.description: This home was recently fully remodeled.  With all new flooring through out the entire home, all new updated bathrooms and kitchen.  Walking up to the home you will find a nice sitting/garden area to your left.  When you enter the home you have a nice sitting area to your left that over looks the front outdoor sitting area or garden.  The kitchen that is perfectly centered in the middle of the home allows easy access to any side of the home and allows for easy entertaining from the dinning room, living room and looking out to the pool area.  In the kitchen you will find the range over looking in the living room making entrainment a breeze. As you walk in the master bedroom you will finding sliding doors to your right that access the pool area and leading to the master bathroom you will find his and her closets on your left and right with a double vanity and walk in shower. Look no further, if your looking for a place to call home this is it. AC has recently been repaired and roof is less than 10 years olf.
